      "span_text": "In agreement with a previous observation showing that SIRT1 negatively regulates p66shc expression [CITATION_1] , our data further show that compared with the combined DOX+Ber group, the Ber-induced downregulation of p66shc and upregulation of SIRT1 were significantly attenuated by EX527 (Figure 3(b) )."
